 firm based in los angeles leonard green  partners which obtained a majority stake contents  history  see also  references  external links historyedit garrett boone and kip tindell met while working in the paint department of montgomery ward the first store location outside texas opened in atlanta georgia in april  by december  the chain had grown to  stores in operation in october  its first new york metropolitan area store opened as of november  it had  locations and reached  with the opening of the first los angeles area location in october  following the deal with leonard green  partners announced in july  the company announced plans to open  more stores in the next five years the first arkansas location little rock opened in march  followed by the first arizona location scottsdale in the summer and the first minnesota location edina and second ohio location cincinnati that fall relevant – discuss as of may  the container store has  locations with plans to open several stores in the following months on may  the company announced that kip tindell would be stepping down as ceo and would be succeeded by coo and president melissa reiff see alsoedit hold everything store chain that closed in  organized living chain that closed in  storables referencesedit  store locator at containerstorecom  a b why container stores founder is quitting ceo job at fortunecom  the container store at fortunecom  hoovers inc fact sheet on the container store  container stores workers huddle up to help you out usa today apr   retrieved oct     containerstorecom about us retrieved   howell arnesa a june   lessons from a colossal cleanup cnnmoneycom retrieved oct     the container store fortune  retrieved    container store put on market retailer wants to use equity but preserve workplace culture the dallas morning newskrt february    container store agrees to partner with leonard green the new york times july   retrieved oct     a b container store says expansion plan on track the dallas m